===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|obsolete}} Any of the [[plant#Noun|plants]] known as [[mercury]], especially the [[annual mercury]] or {{vern|French mercury}} (''[[Mercurialis annua]]''). {{defdate|13th–17th c.}}
# {{lb|en|astrology}} A person [[born]] under the [[influence#Noun|influence]] of the [[planet]] [[Mercury]]. {{defdate|from 16th c.}}
# {{lb|en|chemistry}} A [[chemical compound]] [[contain]]ing [[mercury]].
# {{lb|en|medicine|historical}} A [[preparation]] of mercury, especially as a [[treatment]] for [[syphilis]]. {{defdate|from 17th c.}}

